profile:
A Glass Act has been providing window cleaning, Gutter cleaning, Gutter repairs, interior Painting, exterior Painting, drywall repairs, chandelier cleaning, pressure washing, power washing, house washing, building cleaning exterior, roof cleaning, roof de-mossing, roof moss control treatments, concrete & Paving stone sealing, post construction cleaning, pre-occupany cleaning and a variety of other building maintenance services in the Vancouver area since 1988. 

****

We are pleased to announce that effective July 1, 2015, all of our cleaning services are now available to residents and business' in the Victoria & the Saanich Peninsula area! 

****

COVID-19 STATEMENT

COVID-19 has been declared a pandemic. Federal, provincial and local governments and their agencies have been announcing daily recommendations and restrictions that affect the everyday lives of every Canadian.

Whereas the health authorities are still stating that the risk of contracting the virus is low to moderate in BC, the health and safety of our staff and customers is a paramount concern for us at A Glass Act Window Cleaners & Building Maintenance.

We would ask that customers postpone in booking any INTERIOR CLEANING appointments with us until such time that the major Canadian health authorities announce that it will be safer for us to be working indoors (in your homes) in a more contained proximity to our customers.  We will continue to provide our EXTERIOR CLEANING services at this time while following the very important social distancing regulations.

In addition, we are requiring our staff to self-isolate if they become ill or if someone in their household becomes ill.  We do look forward to providing you with our exterior Spring cleaning service, to get your home or business looking refreshed and clean for the season.  We know that many of you will be spending more time in your yards, gardens and patios this Spring while staying at home.  We look forward to making your building exteriors cleaner and brighter while we all stay safer and healthy at home!!

Thank you for your understanding and support.

Kirby Koochin
(President)
A Glass Act Window Cleaners and Building Maintenance Ltd.

profile:
Sparkle Team is a strata and residential home cleaning service providing over 30 years experience to the Lower Mainland. We guarantee high quality service and custom home care to the Maple Ridge, Pitt Meadows, Langley, and Tri-Cities areas with a 100% satisfaction guarantee.
Our team is well trained, enthusiastic, and motivated to provide innovative home cleaning techniques and go above and beyond your expectations. Sparkle Team will work around your busy schedule, providing flexible appointments, including same day bookings, and will create a personalized cleaning service program to accommodate almost any budget. We offer custom designed home cleaning services to fit the specific needs of your house and family that combine easy payment options and terms including senior discounts.
Sparkle Team caters to those in need of home cleaning pre or post parties and events, move in or move outs, one-time deep home cleans, occasional housekeeping, seasonal maid services, or a flexible permanent schedule for weekly, biweekly, or monthly cleaning service.  Our service checklist allows complete transparency, and a direct link back to the team that services your home.

****


Sparkle Team is confident and guarantees consistent, reliable, and professional high quality cleaning service in every home. If you are unsatisfied with the level of service delivered, contact Sparkle Team within 24 hours of your service appointment and Sparkle Team will return to the home to resolve the issue. Sparkle Team forms a unique relationship with our clients that allows for open communication between us to be sure all the clients expectations are met. We take a genuine interest in the customer’s home, and provide ideas to the homeowner to help maintain a healthy and clean environment.
Sparkle Team has a 10/10 Homestars Rating, is A+ BBB rated, and all employees are bonded and insured.  Each employee is background checked and will always provide home cleaning services in uniform. Keys are coded without your personal information and secured. Keys are never sent via mail, but returned in person by a Sparkle Team owner. Client confidentiality is a priority for us.

****

Don’t spend your valuable personal time cleaning your home.  Allow Sparkle Team to do the job right and give you and your family the freedom to do the things you love!
